import React from 'react'; import moment from "moment"; import windIncon from "./icons/wind2.ico" ; import humidity from "./icons/waterdrop.ico"; import precipitation from "./icons/rain.ico"; function Todayweather (props) { return(

{props.City}

{moment().format("dddd "+'LL')}

{Math.round(props.temperature)}°C

{Math.round(props.Wind)} mph

{Math.round(props.Humidity)} %

{props.Description}

) } export default Todayweather;
